# Cloudflare Pages Redirects and Rewrites
# Optimizes SPA routing and API requests

# API Routes - Proxy to Cloudflare Workers/Functions
# These are handled by the /functions directory automatically
# No explicit redirects needed - Cloudflare Pages handles this

# SPA Fallback - All non-file requests go to index.html
# This enables client-side routing for React Router
# The 200 status code ensures proper SPA behavior
/*    /index.html   200

# Alternative format with explicit path matching
# /accounts    /index.html   200
# /dividends   /index.html   200
# /transactions /index.html   200
# /fund/*      /index.html   200
